OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA wet morning to come with a
OL,6,Fspell of heavy rain moving eastwards
OL,7,Facross the region. The rain will
OL,8,Fgradually clear after lunchtime with
OL,9,Fthe afternoon turning drier and
OL,10,Fbrighter, allowing some sunny spells
OL,11,Fto develop. Feeling rather cool.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLargely dry this evening with
OL,14,Fsome clear spells. Cloud will tend to
OL,15,Fincrease overnight with some showers
OL,16,Fdeveloping towards the early hours. A
OL,17,Frather chilly night for June.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
