OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA day of sunshine and
OL,6,Fscattered showers across the region.
OL,7,FThe showers turning heavy in places,
OL,8,Fbut some lengthier drier spells also
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Remaining on the rather
OL,10,Fcool side.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FFurther sunshine and showers
OL,14,Fthroughout Wednesday before a spell of
OL,15,Fwet and windy weather moves in for
OL,16,FThursday. A return to showers on
OL,17,FFriday, but perhaps turning drier
OL,18,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
